]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div data-parent="true" class="vc_row row-container" id="row-unique-8"><div class="row limit-width row-parent"><div class="wpb_row row-inner"><div class="wpb_column pos-top pos-center align_left column_parent col-lg-12 single-internal-gutter"><div class="uncol style-light"  ><div class="uncoltable"><div class="uncell no-block-padding" ><div class="uncont"><div class="uncode_text_column" ><div class="uncode-single-media  zoooom text-center animate_when_almost_visible alpha-anim"><div class="single-wrapper" style="max-width: 100%;"><div class="tmb tmb-light  tmb-shadowed tmb-shadowed-darker-std tmb-media-first tmb-media-last tmb-content-overlay tmb-no-bg"><div class="t-inside"><div class="t-entry-visual"><div class="t-entry-visual-tc"><div class="uncode-single-media-wrapper"><img class="wp-image-2967" src="https://www.idlewildlodge.org/wp-content/uploads/idlewild-archive-document-Document-c.-1950-Boyd-Jones-Christmas-Card-Page-2.jpg" width="2000" height="1475" alt=""></div>
					</div>
				</div></div></div></div></div>

</div></div></div></div></div></div><script id="script-row-unique-8" data-row="script-row-unique-8" type="text/javascript" class="vc_controls">UNCODE.initRow(document.getElementById("row-unique-8"));</script></div></div></div><div data-parent="true" class="vc_row row-container" id="row-unique-9"><div class="row limit-width row-parent"><div class="wpb_row row-inner"><div class="wpb_column pos-top pos-center align_left column_parent col-lg-12 single-internal-gutter"><div class="uncol style-light"  ><div class="uncoltable"><div class="uncell no-block-padding" ><div class="uncont"><div class="uncode_text_column text-lead" ></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">
 
<span style="font-size: 25px;"><strong>c. 1950 &#8211; Boyd Jones Christmas Card &#8211; Page 2</strong></span>


<br>
A Christmas card from the Boyd Jones family, who owned the Appleby Motel from 1949 - 1952.

<br>
<br>
<span style="font-size: 20px;"><i><strong>Transcription</strong></i></span> 



<br>
<i>"Greetings from the Rockies, Where mighty canons yawn, Where Santa Claus gets the evergreens, To hang our Christmas presents on. Here's a Christmas wish for each snow clad peak, That pierces the western sky, And mountains of good things wished for you, Each day as the year rolls by. The Boyd Jones Family"</i>


<br><br>
<span style="font-size: 20px;"><i><strong>People</strong></i></span> 
<br>






Boyd Jones


<br>





<br>
<span style="font-size: 20px;"><i><strong>Details</strong></i></span> 


<br>
<i>Date: c. 1950</i>


<br>
<i>Location: USA, Colorado, Loveland, Idlewild</i>




<br>
<i>Source: Dauth Family Archive</i>


<br>


<i>Permalink:</i>
<a href="https://www.idlewildlodge.org/document/c-1950-boyd-jones-christmas-card-page-2/">https://www.idlewildlodge.org/document/c-1950-boyd-jones-christmas-card-page-2/</a>


<br><br>
<span style="font-size: 20px;"><i><strong>Related Posts</strong></i></span> 
<br>




<a href='https://www.idlewildlodge.org/posts/appleby-motel/'>Appleby Motel</a>




